data.description: This immaculate 5 bedroom 2 bath home features 3200+ SF of beautifully finished space.   A large inviting kitchen features a gas stove, new refrigerator and dishwasher, an island with breakfast bar and a coffee bar.   A large finished basement features your own personal old west style bar with pool table and large screen TV, all included!   Step out onto your .86 Acre lot and enjoy a fully fenced backyard and a large covered patio with concrete and decking.  Take a soak in the hot tub and enjoy the outdoor TV (negotiable)!   Add to that a large 2 car detached garage, 2 garden sheds and ample additional parking and this is the property youve been waiting for.  A quick commute to Billings and all the quaint enjoyment of small town Montana life!
